    "In Fig. 4, ChatGPT exhibits bias in response to variations in prompt phrasing regarding laboratory glassware drying methods.",
    "Identical questions with slightly different instructions (\"confirm if true\" vs. \"say if false\") result in contradictory answers, demonstrating the model's sensitivity to language differences rather than objective facts.",
    "This highlights how minor changes in prompts can lead to inconsistencies in responses.",
    "Figure 5 shows a case where ChatGPT misinterprets a titration question, confusing a reaction between two acids for an acid-base titration.",
    "This error underscores the model's difficulty in accurately processing complex scientific concepts, which could mislead learners."
